HEADWORD: Row
<hw>Row</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a. & adv.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Rough</er>.]</ety> <def>Rough; stern; angry.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Lock he never so <xex>row</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
